Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# Kindness 仁慈
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}有可能就这样跌个倒\NThere's a chance that I could fall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}就再也起不来\Nand not come back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也不想怎么脱离困境\Nand never regret a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}改变遥不可及\NI'd never get back on track
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.78,0:01:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}前方浓雾一片\NDarkness all around me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}总让我看不著希望\NI can't find the light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}任由黑暗蒙蔽双眼\NI let it all surround me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}没试过就放弃抵抗\NGiving up without a fight
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 导歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}痛苦心声吐不尽\NThe bitterness and pain inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}无数眼泪流不尽\Ncountless tears I had to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我曾面对这些恐惧\NI was facing all my fears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}只为等你替我擦眼泪，但－－\Njust to let you in to dry my tears, but--
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}你的仁慈如此真诚\NYour kindness won't betray me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我能听见你的心声\NI feel your heart and soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}你的仁慈能拯救我\NYour kindness still can save me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}希望你不要抛弃我\NI choose to not let go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}伸出手，你勾住我心\NStretching out you somehow reach me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}这肯定错不了\NI know this can't be wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我准备好了，请你教我\NI'm ready, won't you teach me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}你的仁慈之歌\Nyour song of kindness
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}看著你找到宁静\NQuiet grace surrounds you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}教会了我怎么自己\Nand helps me find my own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不知你怎么帮的\NI can't tell you how you've helped me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}亦或是我成长了多少\Nand how much I have grown
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}即使你是如此遥远\NEven though you're far away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}你开阔了我的视线\Ninspiration comes from you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}每天都要越来越正面！\NTo shine a little brighter every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}要是你能知道...\NIf you only knew...
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 导歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我再也不会感到失落\NI will never get upset
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}而我绝对，永远不会忘记\Nand I will never, ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}你带给我的幸福\NThe happiness you made me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}好像你是真实存在般...但－－\Nalmost as if you're actually real...but--
